[[!meta title="That One Fate Sample In That One Weeknd Track On House Of Balloons"]]

There is a track on the 2011 mixtape from The Weeknd [[!wikipedia House of
Balloons]] called _Coming Down_. The track samples dialogue from Fate/ Stay
Night Episode 21.

